<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/43822013-stolen"><img alt="Stolen: Five Free Boys Kidnapped into Slavery and Their Astonishing Odyssey Home" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1569152792l/43822013._SX98_.jpg" />
